== Pronunciation ==
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /'nip(@)l/

== Noun ==

'''nipple''' (plural [[nipples]])

# The projection of a [[mammary gland]] from which, on females, [[milk]] is secreted.
# An artificial nipple used for bottle-feeding infants.
# A mechanical device through which liquids can be passed in a regulated manner.
# A short tube threaded at both ends, used as a connector.

